            <bug_when>2008-09-26 09:58:24 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>Lets make sure IE8 is sufficiently supported, even before a final IE8 release. While there might still be issues just on the IE8 side, it could help find any qooxdoo-specific problems.

By the time of testing, the latest version should be used, e.g. IE8 Beta 2:
http://blogs.msdn.com/ie/archive/2008/09/16/internet-explorer-8-beta-2-now-available-in-25-languages.aspx</thetext>
          </long_desc>
